acter-husn-khuluq","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-humanity","tag-inheritance-al-faraid","tag-manners-adab","tag-neighbors","tag-rights-al-huquq"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-eq","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/gabriel-emphasizes-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":894,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Gabriel emphasizes good behavior to neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel did not stop instructing me to treat neighbors well until I thought he would make them my heirs.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6015, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2625 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/until-i-thought-heirs\/","url_meta":{"origin":894,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Until I thought he would make them my heirs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel kept advising me to be good to neighbors until I thought he would make them my heirs.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u